{
 "name": "RPlog_Escape_from_Kessel",
 "title": "Escape from Kessel",
 "summary": "Aboard a prison transport bound for Kessel, the captured smuggler Jaspar Andromidas waits in his cell as explosions rock the ship and a boarding raid plunges the corridors into smoke and emergency lighting. Through the haze strides the flamboyant Rattataki pirate Captain Vane (Shiari), who blasts open his cell, arms him, and announces she has been paid handsomely to break him out. Ignoring the other prisoners' pleas, the pair fight their way toward Vane's ship, trading quips even as a pair of stormtroopers gun down some of Vane's crew and knock her flat with a chest hit. Jaspar, dodging fire with practiced ease, and a recovered Vane cut the troopers down, and Vane mourns her fallen pirates before pressing on with the rest of her crew covering their retreat. Jaspar learns the Republic is footing his rescue bill and floats joining forces as they board the Hardlace and detach amid a starfighter battle; the ship jumps to lightspeed, with Vane already turning to collect the favor Jaspar now owes her.",
